2011-03-14T05:59:20Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-14/clover-industries-of-south-africa-first-half-profit-jumps-almost-eightfold.html
  Clover Industries Ltd. (CLR)  said fiscal
first-half earnings before one-time items from continuing
operations increased to 94 million rand from 12 million rand a
year earlier.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
